rgin-left: 25px;\">是一种解释性脚本语言（代码不进行<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/item/%E9%A2%84%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">预编译</a>）。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_16168\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\" href=\"http://\">&nbsp;</a></div></li><li class=\"list-num-1-2 list-num-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 25px;\">主要用来向<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/item/HTML\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">HTML</a>（<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/item/%E6%A0%87%E5%87%86%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%A0%87%E8%AE%B0%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decoration-line: none;\">标准通用标记语言</a>下的一个应用）页面添加交互行为。<span style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 0; position: relative; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 2px; color: rgb(51, 102, 204); cursor: default; padding: 0px 2px;\">[4]</span><a class=\"sup-anchor\" name=\"ref_[4]_16168\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); position: relative; top: -50px; font-size: 0px; line-height: 0;\" href=\"http://\">&nbsp;</a></div></li><li class=\"list-num-1-3 list-num-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style: none;\"><div class=\"para\" label-module=\"para\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: 24px; zoom: 1; margin-left: 25px;\">可以直接嵌入HTML页面，但写成单独的<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://baike.baidu.com/item/js/10687961\" data-lemmaid=\"10687961\" style=\"color: rgb(19, 110, 194); text-decorati